title: The Second Touch | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Second Touch | Joel Osteen
description:
You may feel like you've reached your limits, but get ready; a second touch is coming. God is about to strengthen you to reach the fullness of your destiny. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
